
***********************************************************************************
Version 0.2.3, 30 Oct 2014

Added hpd(), a utility for finding highest posterior density intervals for unimodal
density functions.  Added the 'nJobs' argument to plotFun() for parallel 
processing.  Added doCallParallel(), a wrapper for parallelizing function calls
over vector inputs.

***********************************************************************************
Version 0.2.2, 20 Oct 2014

Added select(), a function for subsetting matrices or dataframes by rows or columns
and returning a matrix or dataframe if only a single row or column was selected.

***********************************************************************************
Version 0.2.1, 8 Oct 2014

Added ifelse1(), a non-vectorized version of ifelse(). Also added plotFun(), for
plotting one or more functions over a common domain.

***********************************************************************************
Version 0.2.0, 30 Sep 2014

Added sed_insert(), sed_replace(), sed_substitute(), streamEdit() for easy sed-like
editing of text files (or character vectors).

Added more(), a function to quickly show the contents of a text file on the
console.

***********************************************************************************
Version 0.1.1, 08 Aug 2014

Modified loadObject() so that the .Rdata file can contain more than one object,
in which case loadObject() returns a list.

***********************************************************************************
Version 0.1.0, 06 Aug 2014

These functions were lifted from the pnlStat package in prepraration for pushing
this package to CRAN.

